  "steps": [
    {
      "title": "Step 1",
      "body": "Cut 1x2 wall cleats to fit the depth of your closet space. Two cleats per shelf."
    },
    {
      "title": "Step 2",
      "body": "Attach 1x2 cleats to wall using construction adhesive and 2\" finish nails. Be sure to use a level and keep cleats in pairs.",
